data.text: @OurbabyMinx @michaelbsacks Yeah, that's true. Yet most celebrities are able to find relationships, so I don't think it's that difficult.

@OurbabyMinx @michaelbsacks 2/ For me, when I see someone young like that looking to marry someone much older, I tend to think there are some emotional issues there related to wanting her father's love, and it usually tends to not work out in the long run. So I'm just glad she got out of it.

@OurbabyMinx @michaelbsacks Yes, you're right. I was thinking he was in his 50's. What do you mean by "her lifestyle"? She seems to have a normal celebrity, rich person lifestyle. Something weird about it?
@OurbabyMinx @michaelbsacks Yeah, but he's like 30 years older than her . Frankly I'm glad they split up.
@OurbabyMinx @michaelbsacks Last I heard they were actually engaged to be married! That was a few months ago.
@michaelbsacks I thought they were engaged? Well, anyway, I'm happy to hear about this.
@michaelbsacks @usweekly He doesn't have a scarf in that picture. That must have been the beginning of the end.
@michaelbsacks Well, no one could have seen THAT coming!
@michaelbsacks Maybe she finally watched Requiem for a Dream and got freaked out.
@michaelbsacks Wait...what? They had been dating? Did Jennifer lose a dare? What was their celeb mash-up name? This all ended too soon!!!
